          <td style="text-align: right" valign="top">Description:</td>
          <td>This test checks the 'minsize' and 'maxsize' attributes which
apply to stretchy operators.  This test checks that inheritance
through the &lt;mstyle> element works, and that percentages work
for CSS units.</td>
